data.description: Beautifully remodeled waterfront home on Vesper Lake! You will be amazed by the stunning lake views throughout, hardwood flooring, and open kitchen layout that features granite counter tops, white shaker cabinets, and stainless-steel appliances. The main floor offers 3 bedrooms, including a gorgeous master suite with walk in closet and master bath. Relax by the gas fireplace and enjoy a breathtaking sunset. The walk-out lower level offers additional living space along with another full bath, sauna, and utility room. This home is perfect for entertaining. The exterior has a large deck overlooking the lake, nice sized yard, shoreline for fishing and paddle boats, and a parklike setting that complete this 1.67-acre home. Other updates include a newer roof (2 years) and high efficiency furnace. Located in Bath Township and tucked away on a quiet and private setting, but also close to everything! This home truly has so much to offer. Schedule your showing today!
